CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Phoenix Asia operates its business primarily through its indirectly wholly-owned Operating Subsidiary, Winfield Engineering (Hong Kong) Limited. We mainly engage in substructure works, such as site formation, ground investigation and foundation works, in Hong Kong. To a lesser extent, we also provide other construction services such as structural steelworks.
